## ğŸ“¦ Summary Table

| Interface       | Takes     | Returns   | Use Case               |
| --------------- | --------- | --------- | ---------------------- |
| `Predicate<T>`  | `T`       | `boolean` | Filters, conditions    |
| `Function<T,R>` | `T`       | `R`       | Mapping, conversion    |
| `Consumer<T>`   | `T`       | `void`    | ForEach, side effects  |
| `Supplier<T>`   | `nothing` | `T`       | Factory, fallback data |

